org.gradoop.flink.model.impl.operators.matching.single.cypher.pojos

Class Embedding

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.gradoop.flink.model.impl.operators.matching.single.cypher.pojos.Embedding
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, org.apache.flink.core.io.IOReadableWritable, org.apache.flink.types.CopyableValue<Embedding>, org.apache.flink.types.Value

    public class Embedding
extends Object
implements org.apache.flink.types.Value, org.apache.flink.types.CopyableValue<Embedding>
    This class represents an Embedding, an ordered List of Embedding Entries. Every entry is either a reference to a single Edge or Vertex, or a path (Edge, Vertex, Edge, Vertex, ..., Edge). The reference is stored via the elements ID. Additionally the embedding ca store an ordered list of PropertyValues.
